 derzeit verhandelten Dimensionen von Körperwissen - Wissen über, im und am Körper - um das Wissen durch den Körper.  aWhat do we know through the body? An broadening of perspectives on the sociology of the body shows that the body is a fundamental category of the social.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aHuman body (Philosophy) 0aMind and body. 0aPhilosophy of mind. 0aSocial interaction. 4aGeorge Lakoff. 4aGesellschaft. 4aInteraktion. 4aMark Johnson. 4aMetapher. 4aSozialität. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aWissen. 4aWissenssoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aGeorge Lakoff.  aInteraction.  aKnowledge.  aMark Johnson.  aMetaphor.  aSocial Relations.  aSociety.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology of Knowledge.  aSociology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2016z9783110485332oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070101208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839434574zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839434574423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839434574/original  a978-3-11-070100-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  a978-3-11-070101-2  PP Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DSWb2016  a